claim.claim-text:
1. A method for recording voice messages while simultaneously projecting light outwardly from a user during inspection of a surrounding area, said method comprising the steps of: 
(a) activating a light contained within an assembly housing of a combination handheld flashlight and audio recorder assembly; 
(b) while carrying the handheld flashlight and audio recorder assembly, projecting the light outwardly from the user to the surrounding area; 
(c) while inspecting the surrounding area, delivering voice messages to an audio recorder contained within the assembly housing; and 
(d) electronically recording the voice messages for subsequent playback by the user.
